{"id": "3850", "revid": "52407671", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3850", "title": "Pouncer", "text": "The Pouncer appears to be an adolescent &lt;a href=\"Hunter\"&gt;Hunter&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Shrieker\"&gt;Shrieker&lt;/a&gt; that can be found on &lt;a href=\"Difficulty\"&gt;Easy difficulty and higher&lt;/a&gt;.\nPouncers will use their wings to help leap great distances and attack using their claws and sharp tongues. This bug has a slightly higher threat level due to its ability to cover a large distance with its jump. \nThey often appear in swarms of other Pouncers, &lt;a href=\"Scavenger\"&gt;Scavengers&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Bile%20Spitter\"&gt;Bile Spitters&lt;/a&gt;. but are easily dealt with. Like most Terminids, Pouncers can cause a Bug Breach if left alive, allowing more threatening Terminids to appear.\nBehavior.\nPouncers will use their wings to aid in their leaps, however they are not the most accurate leapers, and will often under- or overshoot their target.\nWhen not leaping, they will approach Helldivers in as direct a path as possible, climbing over terrain and obstacles in an attempt to attack with their claws and stylets (tongues).\nPouncers will occasionally attempt to leap sideways to avoid incoming fire.\nPouncers are able to release a cloud of pheromones into the air that causes a Bug Breach."}
