{"id": "5942", "revid": "46883485", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5942", "title": "Rasp", "text": " is one of the six planets that reside within the &lt;a href=\"Gallux%20Sector\"&gt;Gallux Sector&lt;/a&gt;.\nTopography.\nSimilar to &lt;a href=\"Fenrir%20III\"&gt;Fenrir III&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Maia\"&gt;Maia&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Claorell\"&gt;Claorell&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Curia\"&gt;Curia&lt;/a&gt;.\nHistory.\nSecond Galactic War.\nReturn of the Illuminate.\nRasp was an isolated lunar colony in the Gallux Sector, far off in the Southern Galactic Rim. Having been settled after the &lt;a href=\"First%20Galactic%20War\"&gt;First Galactic War&lt;/a&gt;, its history was riddled with little events of importance and its economy, while also rather standard and unremarkable, still was robust enough to allow for the construction of urbanized settlements on its meteor showered surface.\nHowever, an envious foe stared from within the darkness of the cosmos, awaiting the opportunity to strike. On December 24th, 2184; amidst the celebration of the Festival of Reckoning that, the attacked. The foe that had once been thought defeated had returned from apparent extinction and was now dead set on plundering the resources of the southern sectors while abducting its citizens. However, the Helldivers would immediately heed the call for aid, standing as Humanity's bulwark against the darkness.\nHaving recently defended the &lt;a href=\"Umlaut%20Sector\"&gt;Umlaut Sector&lt;/a&gt; against the tyrannical Terminids, they now had all the time and motivation needed to deal a decisive blow to the nefarious squids."}
