{"id": "4634", "revid": "37419324", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4634", "title": "Ship Master", "text": "The Ship Master is voiced by &lt;a href=\"https%3A//www.imdb.com/name/nm2800003/%3Fref_%3Dnv_sr_srsg_0_tt_0_nm_8_q_Michelle%252520Wong\"&gt;Michelle Wong&lt;/a&gt;.\nShe is the woman who stands in the Middle of the ship holding a tablet with a terrain map grid on it.\nThe Ship Master is the chief of staff aboard the Super Destroyer. According to her own voicelines, she is the one in charge of coordinating the Super Destroyer's crew during missions in order to deploy all the stratagems that the Helldivers request during deployment. Between deployments, the Ship Master monitors the crew's behavior and well-being, making sure that the Super Destroyer is well maintained and supplied and making sure that the crew is efficient and remains with high morale. \nIt can be safely assumed that the Ship Master is the superior officer of the Service Technician, but is equal in rank to the &lt;a href=\"Democracy%20Officer\"&gt;Democracy Officer&lt;/a&gt; and the Helldivers themselves.\nAlongside the &lt;a href=\"Service%20Technician\"&gt;Service Technician&lt;/a&gt;, she is one of 2 crew members to not hail from Super Earth, instead hailing from an unknown planet colony."}
{"id": "3757", "revid": "54345532", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3757", "title": "Ship Modules", "text": "Ship modules are upgrades to the player's Destroyer which permanently improve the performance of &lt;a href=\"Stratagems\"&gt;Stratagems&lt;/a&gt;. They can be found at the ship management menu at the Patriotic Administration Center and are purchased using &lt;a href=\"Currencies\"&gt;Samples and Requisition Slips&lt;/a&gt; found during missions. Modules only affect the player who purchased them and will visually change parts of the Destroyer depending on which module is upgraded.\nThere are currently 6 Modules, all of which improve different stratagems while visually changing parts of the &lt;a href=\"Super%20Destroyer\"&gt;Super Destroyer&lt;/a&gt;; each of which have 5 available upgrade tiers. \nThe current total cost to fully upgrade everything is: &lt;br&gt;\n 3,830 Common Samples&lt;br&gt; 2,920 Rare Samples&lt;br&gt; 305 Super Samples&lt;br&gt; 335,000 Requisition Slips\n&lt;br&gt;\nClick the images below to display their related information\nPatriotic Administration Center&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\nOrbital Cannons&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\nHangar&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\nBridge&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\nEngineering Bay&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\nRobotics Workshop&lt;br&gt;\n__NOEDITSECTION__"}
