{"id": "3810", "revid": "34624864", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3810", "title": "Upload Escape Pod Data", "text": "&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\nUpload Escape Pod Data is a Tactical Objective that can be found as a mission's primary objective on difficulties Trivial (1) - Medium (3); and found as a secondary/tactical objective on Challenging (4) and higher. It is one three tactical objectives that have no positive or negative effects on the current mission and is one of the easiest objectives to complete.\nWhen the Helldiver reaches the objective they can see an escape pod slightly larger than a Helldiver Drop Pod has crash landed into the surface of the planet. When the Helldiver reaches a close vicinity of the escape pod, they'll be notified that an objective stratagem is available and they must input the specific code to begin uploading the data from the escape pod to command. The uploading process takes roughly 30 seconds to complete and the Helldiver must stay within a short radius around the escape pod itself. Once the upload is complete, the Helldiver can leave the area and either extract if it's a primary objective, or continue on with their mission if it is a secondary objective.\nNotes.\n&lt;br&gt;"}
